{"word":"ἀναζωπυρέω","slug":"ἀναζωπυρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναζωπυρέω</b></el> <p/><i>to rekindle</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to gain fresh life and courage</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; so, <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}